			Company Description 


			J.Jill, Inc. operates as a retailer of women's apparel, accessories and footwear. The company markets its products through direct and retail channels under the J.Jill brand. It offers clothing products including misses, petites, women's and tall. The company was founded on February 17, 2011 and is h...
		


                J.Jill, Inc. operates as a retailer of women's apparel, accessories and footwear. The company markets its products through direct and retail channels under the J.Jill brand. It offers clothing products including misses, petites, women's and tall. The company was founded on February 17, 2011 and is headquartered in Quincy, MA.
            




